Bayer Was Attacked by ‘Anonymous’ Hacker Group, DPA-AFX Says

-- B y   H o l g e r   E l f e s
-- 
2011-07-01T16:34:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-01/bayer-was-attacked-by-anonymous-hacker-group-dpa-afx-says.html
Bayer AG (BAYN) ,  Germany ’s largest
drugmaker, has been attacked by the “Anonymous” hacker group
and has informed the police,  dpa-afx  reported today, citing an
unidentified spokesman for the company.  Processes that are critical to the running of the business
have so far not been affected, the newswire said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Holger Elfes in Dusseldorf, Germany at 
 helfes@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at   cperri@bloomberg.net  